%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Travel%20nightmare%20across%20the%20northeast%20as%20severe%20weather%20causes%20hundreds%20of%20flight%20cancellations%20and%20delays%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20and%20man%20with%20thumbs%20down%20(left)%3B%20man%20with%20thumbs%20up%20(right)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6903edc9599d46a4ccc13229%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeller%20and%20her%20father-in-law%2C%20happy%20to%20be%20off%20the%20plane%3B%20Frank%20Granati%2C%20eager%20to%20get%20to%20Detroit.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Heller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESevere%20weather%20caused%20travel%20disruptions%20across%20the%20northeast.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWeather%20disruptions%20are%20common%20in%20US%20air%20travel%2C%20often%20causing%20delays%20and%20cancellations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAirlines%20prioritize%20safety%2C%20learning%20from%20past%20incidents%20to%20avoid%20flying%20in%20hazardous%20weather.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-air-lines-implores-congress-government-shutdown-workers-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDelta%20flight%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20LaGuardia%20to%20Detroit%20turned%20into%20a%20quiet%20cheering%20match%20on%20Thursday%20%E2%80%94%20one%20group%20hoping%20for%20takeoff%2C%20the%20other%20hoping%20to%20return%20to%20the%20gate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelta%20flight%201122%20was%20still%20being%20described%20as%20on%20time%20when%20boarding%20began%20around%2012%3A15%20p.m.%20But%20amid%20torrential%20rain%20and%20whipping%20winds%2C%20passengers%20spent%20around%20three%20hours%20slowly%20crawling%20along%20the%20airport%20taxiways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20editor%20in%20chief%20Jamie%20Heller%20was%20onboard%20and%20described%20the%20scene%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Bsports%20showdown%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20airplane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Heller%2C%20retreat%20was%20the%20better%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNever%20will%20I%20be%20happier%20to%20be%20at%20LaGuardia%20than%20when%20I%20deboard%20this%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BI%20already%20missed%20my%20connecting%20flight%20out%20of%20Detroit%2C%20so%20it%20would%20have%20meant%20an%20evening%20at%20a%20Detroit%20hotel%20only%20to%20try%20to%20get%20back%20to%20New%20York%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20her%20nearby%20neighbor%2C%20Frank%20Granati%20from%20eastern%20Long%20Island%2C%20was%20gunning%20for%20a%20completed%20trip%2C%20even%20if%20delayed%2C%20with%20one%20goal%20to%20spend%20Halloween%20with%20his%20granddaughter%2C%20whom%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bthree%20and%20a%20half%20going%20on%20thirty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20I%20shouldn't%20have%20texted%20her%20and%20said%20pappa%20bear%20is%20coming%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20when%20the%20flight's%20fate%20was%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20they%20both%20got%20their%20wish.%20Passengers%20were%20allowed%20to%20deplane%20or%20stay%20on%2C%20and%20the%20aircraft%20eventually%20took%20off%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20make%20it%20to%20Michigan%20more%20than%20five%20hours%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlightaware%20data%20shows%20that%20as%20of%207%20p.m.%20local%20time%20on%20Thursday%2C%20there%20were%20203%20cancellations%20(36%25)%20and%20223%20delays%20(39%25)%20at%20LaGuardia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22delta%20departures%20LaGuardia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6903ee75599d46a4ccc1322d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Delta%20departures%20board%20at%20LaGuardia%20on%20Thursday%20afternoon.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Heller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDelta's%20return%20to%20the%20gate%20is%20standard%20procedure%20because%20federal%20law%20requires%20airlines%20to%20move%20the%20aircraft%20to%20a%20safe%20location%20where%20passengers%20can%20deplane%20before%20the%20three-hour%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirlines%20generally%20follow%20the%20rule%2C%20but%20extreme%20circumstances%20can%20happen%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20Delta%20flight%20that%20sat%20six%20hours%20in%20Savannah%20in%202023%20because%20it%20diverted%20for%20weather%2C%20and%20customs%20staff%20weren't%20available%20to%20let%20passengers%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20just%20one%20of%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faviation-experts-why-its-a-nightmare-to-fly-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eflights%20canceled%20or%20delayed%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20due%20to%20severe%20weather.%20The%20three%20New%20York%20City%20area%20airports%20%E2%80%94%20LaGuardia%2C%20JFK%2C%20and%20Newark%20%E2%80%94%20had%20nearly%20400%20cancellations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20roughly%20200%20flights%20were%20disrupted%20at%20Orlando%2C%20with%20the%20FAA%20citing%20staffing%20issues.%20It's%20among%20the%20airports%20experiencing%20delays%20because%20of%20the%20government%20shutdown%2C%20as%20air%20traffic%20controllers%2C%20who%20are%20working%20without%20pay%2C%20call%20out%20and%20leave%20facilities%20short-staffed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20apologize%20to%20our%20customers%20who%20had%20a%20disruption%20today%20%E2%80%94%20refunds%20are%20due%20to%20anyone%20who%20wants%20one%20if%20a%20flight%20is%20canceled%20and%20they%20chose%20not%20to%20travel%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Delta%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20They%20added%20that%20customers%20are%20rebooked%20automatically%20on%20the%20next%20best%20itinerary.%20Delta%20gave%20Heller%20a%20choice%20of%20credit%20or%20a%20refund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ded9912d-2750-4055-a3c9-becce69f52b8%5C%22%3ESituations%20like%20this%20aren't%20unusual%2C%20and%20they're%20not%20unique%20to%20Delta%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThunderstorms%20in%20spring%20and%20summer%2C%20hurricanes%20in%20fall%2C%20snow%20and%20ice%20in%20winter%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-it-safe-to-fly-in-thunderstorms-snow-windy-weather-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweather%20disruptions%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20part%20of%20how%20flying%20works%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeather%20accounts%20for%20roughly%20three-quarters%20of%20air%20traffic%20delays%20in%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%2C%20particularly%20in%20congested%20corridors%20like%20the%20Northeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20frustrating%20as%20delays%20are%2C%20it's%20always%20better%20to%20miss%20a%20connection%20than%20take%20off%20into%20unsafe%20conditions.%20Airlines%20have%20learned%20that%20the%20hard%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20flight%20by%20now-defunct%20Southern%20Airways%20crashed%20in%201977%20after%20the%20pilots%20flew%20through%20a%20thunderstorm%2C%20while%20a%20Dutch%20airliner%20crashed%20in%201981%20after%20it%20flew%20into%20a%20tornado.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20notable%20cases%20was%20in%201968%2C%20when%20an%20early-age%20jetliner%20crashed%20after%20turbulence%20caused%20an%20in-flight%20structural%20failure.%20Investigators%20determined%20that%20the%20plane%20took%20off%20in%20%26quot%3Ban%20area%20of%20avoidable%20hazardous%20weather%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20swept%20up%20in%20a%20severe%20squall%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20similarly%20severe%20squall%20line%20was%20battering%20the%20Northeast%20on%20Thursday%2C%20bringing%20with%20it%20severe%20rain%20and%20winds%20that%20led%20the%20National%20Weather%20Service%20to%20issue%20a%20flash%20flood%20warning%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThursday's%20travel%20chaos%20wasn't%20a%20failure%20of%20the%20airline%20or%20the%20airport%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20the%20system%20working%20as%20intended%20after%20decades%20of%20lessons%20about%20not%20pushing%20into%20bad%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPilots%2C%20dispatchers%2