raints.%26quot%3B%20Then%2C%20things%20get%20more%20sophisticated%3A%20%26quot%3Bhow%20to%20pivot%20the%20persona%20of%20an%20LLM%20from%20maker%20to%20checker%2C%20or%20how%20to%20use%20two%20LLMs%20to%20debate%20a%20concept%20to%20get%20more%20creative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20transition%20is%20a%20companywide%20endeavor%2C%20with%20workers%20often%20teaching%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20teams%20quickly%20set%20up%20prompt%20libraries%2C%20'prompt%20of%20the%20week'%20emails%2C%20and%20social%20channels%20to%20share%20power-user%20innovations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20get%20the%20technology%20into%20employees'%20hands%20%E2%80%94%20with%20change%20management%20and%20training%20%E2%80%94%20they'll%20be%20best%20positioned%20to%20innovate%20and%20put%20it%20to%20good%20use.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226a57182a-7325-4ad9-b901-7720615db8b9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEveryone%20will%20have%20to%20make%20changes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWaldron%20also%20offered%20insight%20into%20how%20some%20technical%20roles%20are%20learning%20new%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSoftware%20engineers%20need%20to%20be%20upskilled%20to%20build%20scalable%20AI%20systems%20based%20on%20agents%20and%20LLM%20components%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BAnother%20population%20is%20technologists%2C%20who%20will%20increasingly%20want%20to%20build%20sophisticated%20applications%20using%20agentic%20or%20gen%20AI.%20That%20skill%20set%20is%20something%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20trained.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgentic%20AI%20is%20drawing%20significant%20focus%20from%20Wall%20Street%20and%20Silicon%20Valley.%20The%20notion%20that%20semi-autonomous%20digital%20%26quot%3Bagents%26quot%3B%20could%20orchestrate%20end-to-end%20projects%20independently%20has%20been%20polarizing%20in%20some%20quarters.%20But%20at%20a%20conference%20last%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsi