Mark%20Zuckerberg%20said%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bmetaverse%26quot%3B%20eight%20times%20on%20Meta's%20third-quarter%20earnings%20call.%20This%20time%20around%2C%20he%20didn't%20say%20it%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Meta's%20earnings%20call%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20analysts%20asked%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20and%20CFO%20Susan%20Li%20about%20the%20state%20of%20the%20business.%20The%20executives%20spoke%20extensively%20about%20cap-ex%2C%20compute%2C%20and%20advertising%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20metaverse%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-metaverse-crypto-blockchain-gaming-vr-real-estate-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20peak%20priority%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0was%20the%20most%20glaring%20omission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-horizon-worlds-child-safety-whistleblower-ftc-fairplay-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHorizon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Meta's%20virtual%20reality%20platform%2C%20also%20went%20unsaid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20isn't%20giving%20up%20on%20its%20metaverse%20push.%20In%20a%20recent%20memo%20viewed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-cto-andrew-bosworth-reshuffling-metaverse-unit-read-the-memo-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20CTO%20Andrew%20Bosworth%20told%20employees%20about%20a%20shake-up%20in%20the%20division.%20%26quot%3BThe%20priority%20of%20the%20metaverse%20work%20remains%20unchanged%2C%20and%20it%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20companywide%20priority%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBosworth%20had%20previously%20told%20Meta%20staff%20that%20this%20year%20would%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20critical%26quot%3B%20to%20prove%20the%20metaverse%20is%20either%20a%20visionary%20feat%20or%20a%20%26quot%3Blegendary%20misadventure%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-cto-metaverse-reality-labs-legendary-misadventure-memo-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eearlier%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20of%20the%20call%20was%20%26quot%3Bcompute%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20Zuckerberg%20said%2014%20times%2C%20and%20Li%20said%208%20times.%20Other%20words%20related%20to%20Meta's%20AI%20cap-ex%2C%20like%20%26quot%3Binfrastructure%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcapacity%2C%26quot%3B%20bubbled%20up%20at%2012%20references%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20is%20investing%20heavily%20in%20its%20compute%20power%20and%20AI%20infrastructure.%20The%20company%20raised%20its%202025%20capex%20spending%20guidance%2C%20and%20Li%20said%20it%20would%20spend%20even%20more%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20seem%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-microsoft-stock-price-earnings-ai-capex-spending-reaction-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egrowing%20skeptical%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20Meta%20shares%20plunged%20by%20double%20digits%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20also%20repeated%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bnovel%26quot%3B%20seven%20times%2C%20referencing%20the%20pursuit%20of%20novel%20work%20and%20AI%20capabilities.%20As%20Meta%20builds%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexandr-wang-meta-superintelligence-labs-layoffs-memo-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eand%20trims%3C%2Fa%3E)%20its%20superintelligence%20lab%2C%20the%20company%20hopes%20to%20build%20a%20frontier%20model%20with%20truly%20original%20use%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20to%20build%20novel%20models%20and%20novel%20products%2C%20and%20I'm%20excited%20to%20share%20more%20when%20we%20have%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20its%20social%20networks%2C%20Facebook%20got%20the%20most%20shoutouts%20at%2013.%20Instagram%20and%20Threads%20were%20mentioned%2011%20and%2010%20times%2C%20respectively.%20WhatsApp%20trailed%20behind%20at%206%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumer%20hardware%20was%20a%20major%20focus%20of%20the%20call.%20Participants%20said%20%26quot%3Bglasses%26quot%3B%20six%20times%20and%20%26quot%3BQuest%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20Meta's%20virtual%20reality%20headset%20%E2%80%94%20nine%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolitics%20went%20almost%20entirely%20unmentioned%20on%20the%20call.%20Meta%20paid%20a%20%2415.9%20billion%20tax%20charge%20related%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-big-beautiful-bill-impacts-wallet-taxes-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOne%20Big%20Beautiful%20Bill%20Act%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20weighed%20on%20it%20earnings%2C%20though%20the%20company%20said%20it%20expected%20to%20see%20a%20lower%20tax%20rate%20in%20future%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20words%20%26quot%3Bpresident%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BTrump%26quot%3B%20were%20not%20mentioned.%20Previous%20earnings%20calls%20mentioned%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-stock-earnings-call-report-live-updates-2025-4%23zuckerberg-talks-tariffs-kind-of%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emacroeconomic%20uncertainty%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20without%20explicitly%20citing%20tariffs.%20The%20third-quarter%20call%20did%20not%20mention%20such%20uncertainties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20its%20competitors%2C%20neither%20Zuckerberg%20nor%20Li%20on%20the%20call%20name-checked%20OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20Google%2C%20or%20xAI.%20One%20analyst%20did%20mention%20OpenAI's%20viral%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sora-engineer-will-depue-new-team-artificial-superintelligence-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESora%20video%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-earnings-call-analyst-mark-zuckerberg-compute-capacity-metaverse-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%