g%20a%20bottle%20of%20her%20skincare%20line%2C%20Elm%20Biosciences%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6900f343c007ca8c2737c665%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EElm%20Biosciences%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChronic%2C%20low-grade%20inflammation%20%E2%80%94%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20'inflammaging'%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20key%20driver%20of%20visible%20skin%20aging%2C%26quot%3B%20notes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unionderm.com%2Fdoctors%2Fpooja-rambhia-md%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Pooja%20Rambhia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20MD%2C%20a%20New%20York-based%20board-certified%20dermatologist.%20%26quot%3BOver%20time%2C%20inflammation%20leads%20to%20fine%20lines%2C%20wrinkles%2C%20and%20a%20loss%20of%20dermal%20integrity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElm%20Biosciences%20offers%20two%20products%3A%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felmbiosciences.com%2Fproducts%2Fa3o-elemental-serum%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA3O%20Elemental%20Serum%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20skin%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felmbiosciences.com%2Fproducts%2Finner-dose-daily-skin-supplement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInner%20Dose%20Daily%20Skin%20Supplement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20combination%20of%20which%20purports%20to%20reduce%20inflammation%20by%20strengthening%20the%20skin's%20delicate%20barrier%2C%20treating%20UV%20damage%2C%20and%20keeping%20skin%20hydrated.%20Each%20contains%20ingredients%20that%20align%20with%20the%20brand's%20claims%20about%20reducing%20inflammation%2C%20but%20it's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20these%20products%20are%20more%20preventive%20than%20completely%20reparative%20(especially%20the%20supplements).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20a%20lot%20about%20age%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20look%20my%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20Martha%20Stewart%20said%20on%20her%20podcast%20in%202024%20%E2%80%94%20echoing%20what%20she%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fintothegloss.com%2F2015%2F03%2Fmartha-stewart-makeup%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInto%20The%20Gloss%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20in%202015%2C%20that%20she%20knows%20wrinkles%20can't%20be%20erased%20with%20skincare%20alone%2C%20but%20they%20can%20be%20softened%20with%20prevention%20and%20a%20proactive%20routine.%20Dr.%20Rambhia%20explains%20that%20there%20is%20merit%20to%20Stewart's%20approach.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20wrinkles%20form%2C%20topical%20skincare%20alone%20can't%20erase%20them%20completely.%20However%2C%20consistent%20use%20of%20evidence-based%20ingredients%20such%20as%20retinoids%2C%20antioxidants%2C%20and%20daily%20sunscreen%20can%20soften%20their%20appearance%20and%20help%20prevent%20progression.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20does%20that%20translate%20to%20this%20inside-and-out%20approach%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20with%20sensitive%20skin%20who%20would%20love%20to%20prevent%20my%20skin%20from%20aging%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible%2C%20I%20put%20Stewart's%20new%20Elm%20Biosciences%20skincare%20and%20supplement%20line%20to%20the%20test%20to%20see%20if%20the%20antioxidant-rich%20products%20actually%20make%20a%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bfd3d1c5-11ea-4b14-ad52-1974283be251%5C%22%3EMy%20review%3A%20The%20A3O%20Elemental%20Serum%20delivers%20a%20noticeable%20glow%20with%20a%20lightweight%20feel.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Left%3A%20swatch%20of%20the%20serum%5CnRight%3A%20Image%20of%20the%20glass%20serum%20bottle%20with%20silver%20cap%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6900f6e4599d46a4ccc0fea7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EOlivia%20Rose%20Rushing%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EElm's%20serum%20is%20housed%20in%20a%20weighty%2C%20frosted%20glass%20bottle%20with%20a%20golden%20cap%20that%20is%20so%20luxurious%20it's%20almost%20like%20a%20piece%20of%20decor.%20But%20the%20serum%20itself%20is%20just%20as%20luxe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20started%20testing%20it%2C%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20how%20silky-smooth%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felmbiosciences.com%2Fproducts%2Fa3o-elemental-serum%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA3O%20Elemental%20Serum%3C%2Fa%3E%20was.%20The%20formula%20is%20lightweight%20and%20non-sticky%2C%20and%20it%20immediately%20adds%20a%20radiant%2C%20youthful%20glow%20that%20lasts%20for%20hours%20on%20end.%20There's%20no%20smell%20that%20I%20can%20detect%20(which%20is%20a%20major%20bonus%20for%20me)%2C%20and%20the%20subtle%20yellow%20hue%20of%20the%20serum%20creates%20a%20warmth%20on%20my%20skin%20that%20makes%20me%20look%20more%20awake.%20It%20also%20absorbs%20quickly%2C%20making%20it%20work%20extremely%20well%20with%20makeup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20testing%20the%20serum%20for%20nearly%20a%20month%2C%20I've%20found%20that%20my%20skin%20looks%20healthier%20and%20happier%20than%20before%2C%20with%20noticeable%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22221e9c96-b9dd-40e7-a1d5-7132472d5c13%5C%22%3EThe%20serum%20ingredients%20aren't%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20buzzy%20marketing%20terms.%20They're%20actually%20proven%20to%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20skin.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22close-up%20selfie%20of%20author%20after%20using%20Elm%20skincare%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6900f61cc007ca8c2737c6f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EOlivia%20Rose%20Rushing%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20formula%20itself%20hinges%20on%20the%20brand's%20patent-pending%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felmbiosciences.com%2Fpages%2Fscience%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA3O%20Complex%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20a%20combination%20of%20Acetyl%20Zingerone%20(an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1111%2Fics.c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantioxidant%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20in%20ginger)%2C%20Bakuchiol%20(a%20retinol%20alternative)%2C%20and%20a%20hydrating%20fatty%20acid%20ester.%20This%20combination%20is%20designed%20to%20reduce%20skin%20inflammation%20and%20fight%20signs%20of%20aging.%20It%20also%20contains%20well-known%20moisturizing%20and%20brightening%20ingredients%20like%20squalene%2C%20hyaluronic%20acid%2C%20vitamin%20E%2C%20and%20shea%20butter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeveral%20ingredients%20in%20this%20formulation%20align%20with%20the%20product's%20claims%20of%20supporting%20collagen%20development%2C%20strengthening%20the%20skin%20barrier%2C%20and%20improving%20hydration%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Rambhia.%20%26quot%3BBakuchiol%2C%20a%20plant-derived%20retinol%20alternative%2C%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20promote%20collagen%20production%20and%20improve%20skin%20texture%20while%20being%20better%20tolerated%20than%20traditional%20retinoids.%20Additionally%2C%20acetyl%20zingerone%2C%20a%20potent%20antioxidant%20derived%20from%20ginger%2C%20may%20help%20mitigate%20oxidative%20stress%20and%20UV-induced%20damage.%20Collectively%2C%20these%20ingredients%20support%20a%20more%20youthful%20and%20radiant%20complexion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20while%20it's%20true%20you%20might%20be%20paying%20a%20lot%20for%20the%20packaging%2C%20you're%20also%20getting%20a%20formula%20that's%20actually%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2226f7ec09-6b63-498a-b074-849d108e2751%5C%22%3EThe%20Inner%20Dose%20Daily%20Skin%20Supplement%20is%20filled%20with%20vitamin%20D%20and%20antioxidants%2C%20which%20derms%20say%20can%20reduce%20inflammation%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they%20may%20not%20be%20as%20effective%20as%20you're%20led%20to%20think.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22elm%20biosciences%20supplements%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cc6523f9db348adc0bc32b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EOlivia%20Rose%20Rushing%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20typically%20a%20bit%20weary%20of%20supplements%20(I've%20had%20some%20negative%20reactions%20to%20certain%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fvitamins-for-hair-growth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehair%20and%20skin%20gummies%3C%2Fa%3E%20before)%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20thing%20I%20like%20in%20theory%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felmbiosciences.com%2Fproducts%2Finner-dose-daily-skin-supplement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInner%20Dose%20Daily%20Skin%20Supplement%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20just%20how%20simple%20the%20ingredient%20list%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvitamin-d-and-longevity-anti-aging-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVitamin%20D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20known%20to%20strengthen%20the%20skin's%20barrier%20and%20support%20skin%20regeneration%2C%20is%20the%20heaviest%20hitter%2C%20though%20it%20also%20includes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC11009219%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20turmeric%20root%20powder%3C%2Fa%3E%20(a%20famously%20anti-inflammatory%20ingredient)%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC5376420%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eholy%20basil%20leaf%20powder%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20among%20a%20handful%20of%20other%20ingredients%20aimed%20at%20fighting%20aging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20brand%20claims%20the%20supplement%20will%20work%20overtime%20to%20help%20fight%20wrinkle-causing%20inflammation%20from%20the%20inside%2C%20Dr.%20Rambhia%20does%20have%20her%20thoughts%20on%20supplements%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIngestible%20supplements%20can%20play%20a%20supportive%20role%20in%20overall%20skin%20health%2C%20particularly%20when%20addressing%20oxidative%20stress%2C%20inflammation%2C%20or%20nutritional%20deficiencies.%20However%2C%20they%20should%20be%20viewed%20as%20adjunctive%20rather%20than%20primary%20interventions%2C%20%5Bespecially%20considering%20that%5D%20the%20quality%20and%20formulation%20of%20these%20products%20vary%20widely%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20formulation%20includes%20several%20bioactive%20compounds%20with%20demonstrated%20antioxidant%20and%20anti-inflammatory%20activity%3A%20polypodium%20leucotomos%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20reduce%20UV-induced%20oxidative%20stress%20and%20enhance%20the%20skin's%20natural%20defenses%2C%20while%20curcumin%2C%20the%20active%20compound%20in%20turmeric%2C%20exerts%20anti-inflammatory%20effects.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20while%20there's%20evidence%20that%20the%20supplements%20can%20be%20impactful%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20you'll%20see%20any%20drastic%20results%20from%20them.%20I've%20only%20been%20taking%20the%20supplement%20for%20about%20a%20month%2C%20and%20I%20haven't%20noticed%20much%2C%20but%20the%20brand%20notes%20that%20it%20takes%20a%20minimum%20of%20three%20months%20to%20see%20results.%20That%20said%2C%20my%20sister-in-law%20unwittingly%20noticed%20a%20change%20in%20my%20skin%20and%20said%20how%20%26quot%3Brefreshed%26quot%3B%20I%20looked%20%E2%80%94%20which%2C%20for%20a%20tired%20new%20mom%20to%20a%20seven-month-old%20(who%20is%20currently%20teething%20and%20not%20sleeping%20well)%2C%20was%20a%20completely%20unexpected%20compliment.%20Of%20course%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20know%20how%20much%20of%20an%20impact%20the%20supplements%20actually%20had%20here%2C%20because%20the%20results%20of%20the%20serum%20felt%20much%20more%20noticeable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222d1a7b7b-6bd0-438a-a7ab-87740af87a17%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20again%2C%20I'm%20here%20to%20say%3A%20Martha%20Stewart%20has%20good%20taste.%20Her%20foray%20into%20the%20world%20of%20beauty%20is%20no%20different%2C%20and%20Elm%20Biosciences%20is%20a%20solid%20choice%20for%20those%20who%20are%20really%20serious%20about%20their%20skin%20care%20and%20want%20to%20prevent%20signs%20of%20aging%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20serum%20is%20a%20gorgeous%20%E2%80%94%20and%20seriously%20luxe%20%E2%80%94%20addition%20to%20my%20own%20routine%2C%20and%20I'll%20definitely%20be%20continuing%20to%20use%20the%20bottle%20until%20the%20very%20last%20drop.%20Personally%2C%20it%20is%20a%20bit%20pricey%2C%20so%20I%20may%20use%20it%20only%20a%20few%20times%20a%20week%20for%20a%20boost%20of%20radiance%20instead%20of%20every%20day%20to%20savor%20the%20golden%20goodness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20daily%20supplement%2C%20I%20haven't%20seen%20major%20results%20yet%2C%20but%20it's%20filled%20with%20efficacious%20(and%20more%20importantly%2C%20safe)%20ingredients%2C%20so%20it%20feels%20like%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20elevate%20my%20self-care%20game%20in%20a%20unique%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20win%20for%20Stewart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fmartha-stewart-skincare-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761843715000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690399b70be9845f2dc567d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fmartha-stewart-skincare-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20tested%20Martha%20Stewart's%20new%20skincare%20line%2C%20Elm%20Biosciences%2C%20to%20see%20if%20its%20anti-aging%20serum%20and%20supplement%20actually%20deliver%20results.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Olivia%20Rose%20Rushing)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fmartha-stewart-skincare-review%22%2C%22cdnAmp